data.description: Charming 3-bed, 2-bath home with an attached 2-car garage, main level laundry, and an open floor plan. Enjoy outdoor living on the back deck overlooking a fenced yard. Located in the heart of town, you're within walking distance of shops, restaurants, and schools. Modern updates throughout ensure move-in readiness, making it a perfect blend of style and convenience. This meticulously maintained property offers the best of both worlds—modern comfort and a warm, community-oriented neighborhood. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your dream home!
